dc_title_s: Kaisei shinpan Kyōto ku kumi meisaizu: kan; Kamisaka Yoshishige.
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Title on map: Kyōto ku kumi meisaizu. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the left. Relief shown pictorially. Includes distance chart, legend, and index of schools. 1 map: col.; 47 x 70 cm., folded in cover 17 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
